<br>
Also camping Chief Sanre is very good experience all the way to 24, he is also located in the mountain area where the crags are.  Be careful not to attack him near his gnoll friends though because they will gang up on you.<br>
<br>
Finally, Broon is soloable at 23 but with SOW, it's a 50-50 proposition without it.  Good hunting!<br>
